{"tid":651956,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[IT吃香]：資訊科技界十分缺人，人工升幅最劇。","createTime":"2018-05-03T13:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T13:42:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0d6e0ced415893e1cbe5445ab638aa8f2364775d","tid":651956,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:16:33.000Z","msg":"人力資源顧問指，上年度金融及資訊科技界較吃香，人手需求大，故人工升幅最劇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">專家：金融及IT吃香</span><br />\n<br />\n資訊科技界亦十分缺人，因商界越來越着重互聯網發展，金融業亦鼓勵客人多用網上服務及網上保安，帶動業界加人工，估計兩界別一般工資有5至10%增長，若被挖角，人工更有兩至三成增幅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180503/20379815?_ga=2.30421631.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180503%2F20379815%3F_ga%3D2.30421631.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435&d=9taV22dOq6wRUAuP5TGQxWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=4495fcf3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180503%2F20379815%3F_ga%3D2.30421631.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435&h=93c89ac5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180503/20379815?_ga=2.30421631.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435</a>"},{"pid":"2413968c083695119c3b7060bb5c40e92171b0d7","tid":651956,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69bde5c100ff1c5476bf6dc2fe2c405c0d50b0ac","tid":651956,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等老貓出山"},{"pid":"bfd7a62c27c93ea88e887e15015b4e0e7d435e72","tid":651956,"uid":45120,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:19:05.000Z","msg":"IT吃夜香"},{"pid":